    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 猎鹰重型火箭将发射美国卫星追踪太阳风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 的猎鹰重型火箭是世界上最强大的运载火箭之一，它将于周二发射，将一颗新的美国卫星送入轨道，该卫星旨在帮助气象预报员监测大规模太阳风暴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:47:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗将如何选举总统，以及他为何重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/iran-election-who-will-succeed-president-raisi-and-how-will-they-be-chosen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗定于 6 月 28 日举行总统大选，此前易卜拉欣·莱西在一次直升机坠毁事故中丧生。虽然伊朗的最高权力掌握在最高领袖阿亚图拉·阿里·哈梅内伊手中，但总统有时可以利用民众支持、政治关系和与强大机构的联系来影响政策。此次选举正值伊朗与西方关系紧张之际，德黑兰动员了一个地区代理民兵网络来打击]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/iran-election-who-will-succeed-president-raisi-and-how-will-they-be-chosen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:36:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多选举惨败后，特鲁多认为未来还有“艰苦工作”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trudeau-sees-hard-work-ahead-after-shock-toronto-election-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，他听到了选民的“担忧和沮丧”，并誓言在自由党于多伦多补选中惨败后努力解决他们的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trudeau-sees-hard-work-ahead-after-shock-toronto-election-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:32:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢恩鲍姆缓慢推出内阁人选以安抚市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sheinbaum-soothes-markets-with-slow-drip-of-cabinet-picks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当选总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 在投资者眼中开局不利。她在其政党取得压倒性胜利后，越是大谈改革司法系统和通过普选选举法官的计划，投资者抛售墨西哥资产的热情就越高。过去一个月，比索是全球表现最差的货币，已暴跌 8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sheinbaum-soothes-markets-with-slow-drip-of-cabinet-picks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国将向委内瑞拉总统选举派遣选举监督员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/un-to-deploy-electoral-monitors-to-venezuela-presidential-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在委内瑞拉反对派拒绝签署承认总统选举结果的协议几天后，联合国表示将派遣一个由四名专家组成的小组监督委内瑞拉选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/un-to-deploy-electoral-monitors-to-venezuela-presidential-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在总统辩论前放宽禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trump-gag-order-relaxed-in-hush-money-case-after-trial-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约封口费案中针对唐纳德·特朗普的禁言令基本被解除，这让这位前总统在竞选总统期间有了更多的自由来批评诉讼程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trump-gag-order-relaxed-in-hush-money-case-after-trial-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国空军罢免陷入困境的 1310 亿美元洲际弹道导弹项目负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/air-force-ousts-head-of-its-troubled-131-billion-icbm-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国空军已撤换了陷入困境的下一代洲际弹道导弹项目的经理，理由是对该项目的管理“失去信心”，而该项目的成本已飙升至少 37%，达到估计的 1310 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/air-force-ousts-head-of-its-troubled-131-billion-icbm-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利将在欧盟领导人的就业协议中扮演关键角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/italy-set-to-get-key-eu-role-in-leaders-top-jobs-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中间派政党希望在本周晚些时候的欧盟峰会之前就欧盟最高职位达成协议，意大利将有机会在下届欧盟委员会中担任高级职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/italy-set-to-get-key-eu-role-in-leaders-top-jobs-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“这改变了一切”：特鲁多因多伦多失利而受创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-s-conservatives-win-liberal-stronghold-in-blow-to-trudeau</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党赢得多伦多市中心一个选区的特别选举，这对总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的自由党在明年全国选举前造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-s-conservatives-win-liberal-stronghold-in-blow-to-trudeau</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 10:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
